        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Hj2W5uPPpjN2sFp9lBE7-8" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;align=left;" value="N2. Duplication Detection  —  Frontier LLM&#xa;&#xa;Squad 5 about to build phone number validation.&#xa;Squad 1 already built one 2 sprints ago — in production.&#xa;Same problem, same solution, two teams, no awareness.&#xa;&#xa;Alert fired immediately: Squad 1 PO + Squad 5 PO notified." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="540" x="440" y="418" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Hj2W5uPPpjN2sFp9lBE7-9" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;align=left;" value="N3. Dependency Mapping  —  Frontier LLM&#xa;&#xa;Squad 12 needs phone validation for fraud alerts.&#xa;Depends on Squad 1&#39;s validator — but it&#39;s undocumented.&#xa;Squad 12 is blocked, doesn&#39;t know who to ask.&#xa;&#xa;Alert fired: Squad 12 PO + Squad 1 PO + Programme Manager.&#xa;Recommendation: docs + alignment before Sprint 4." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="540" x="440" y="578" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Hj2W5uPPpjN2sFp9lBE7-10" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#e1d5e7;strokeColor=#9673a6;fontSize=10;align=left;" value="N4. Discarded Decision Tracking  —  Frontier LLM&#xa;&#xa;Squad 5 about to add an open-source phone validation library.&#xa;Nexus knows Squad 1 tried that — too slow at scale.&#xa;&#xa;Nexus pushes to Squad 5 Emma live mid-meeting:&#xa;Squad 1 tried that lib. Too slow. Use their custom one. Saves you a week." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="540" x="440" y="738" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Hj2W5uPPpjN2sFp9lBE7-11" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;" value="N5. Constraint Resolution Monitoring  —  Frontier LLM&#xa;&#xa;Squad 1 added support for new country codes in Sprint 3.&#xa;Nexus auto-identifies all squads using their validator.&#xa;&#xa;Broadcast: Squad 5 · Squad 12 · Squad 18&#xa;Validator now supports new countries. Pull latest. No code change needed." vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="130" width="540" x="440" y="898" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Hj2W5uPPpjN2sFp9lBE7-12" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f8cecc;strokeColor=#b85450;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;" value="PO Alert&#xa;Squad 1 + Squad 5&#xa;&#xa;Duplication detected.&#xa;Squad 5 about to rebuild&#xa;Squad 1&#39;s validator.&#xa;Align before sprint commit." vertex="1">
